title: PetSmart 's revenue in the U.S. 2014/15 - 2019/20
summary: Overall Revenue in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Revenue in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2015/16 to 2017/18, and lastly slightly increasing from 2017/18 to 2018/19.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017/18 and 2018/19.
Maximum Revenue in million U.S. dollars, about 6492.5 was reported at Year 2018/19
Minimum Revenue in million U.S. dollars about 5039.7 was reached at Year 2015/16
